msgstr "枚举 **EmissionShape**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_cpuparticles2d.rst:295
msgid ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_POINT** = **0** --- All particles will be emitted from a"
" single point."
msgstr "**EMISSION_SHAPE_POINT** = **0** —— 所有粒子将从一个点发射。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_cpuparticles2d.rst:297
msgid ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_SPHERE** = **1** --- Particles will be emitted on the "
"surface of a sphere flattened to two dimensions."
msgstr "**EMISSION_SHAPE_SPHERE** = **1** —— 粒子将在展平为二维的球体表面上发射。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_cpuparticles2d.rst:299
msgid ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_RECTANGLE** = **2** --- Particles will be emitted in the"
" area of a rectangle."
msgstr "**EMISSION_SHAPE_RECTANGLE** = **2** —— 粒子将在矩形区域内发射。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_cpuparticles2d.rst:301
msgid ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_POINTS** = **3** --- Particles will be emitted at a "
"position chosen randomly among :ref:`emission_points "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_points>`. Particle color will be "
"modulated by :ref:`emission_colors "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_colors>`."
msgstr ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_POINTS** = **3** —— 粒子将在 :ref:`emission_points "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_points>` 中的一个随机选择的位置发射。粒子颜色将由 "
":ref:`emission_colors <class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_colors>` "
"来调制。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_cpuparticles2d.rst:303
msgid ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_DIRECTED_POINTS** = **4** --- Particles will be emitted "
"at a position chosen randomly among :ref:`emission_points "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_points>`. Particle velocity and "
"rotation will be set based on :ref:`emission_normals "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_normals>`. Particle color will be"
" modulated by :ref:`emission_colors "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_colors>`."
msgstr ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_DIRECTED_POINTS** = **4** —— 粒子将在 :ref:`emission_points "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_points>` "
"中的一个随机选择的位置发射。粒子的速度和旋转将基于 :ref:`emission_normals "
"<class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_normals>` 设置。粒子颜色将由 "
":ref:`emission_colors <class_CPUParticles2D_property_emission_colors>` "
"进行调制。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_cpuparticles2d.rst:305
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**EMISSION_SHAPE_MAX** = **5** --- Represents the size of the "
":ref:`EmissionShape <enum_CPUParticles2D_EmissionShape>` enum."
msgstr "**FLAG_MAX** = **3** —— 表示 :ref:`Flags <enum_CPUParticles2D_Flags>` 枚举的大小。"

